Resource Profile: CH VACD Immunization Administration Composition

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-composition-immunization-administration Version: 3.0.0
Active as of 2022-12-21 Computable Name: CHVACDCompositionImmunizationAdministration

Copyright/Legal: CC-BY-SA-4.0

Definition of the composition for the immunization administration document.

Scope and Usage

This composition is defined to use in an immunization administration context. This means to document and/or exchange one or more vaccination given/applied to a referenced patient.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CH VACD Immunization Administration Document
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH VACD Immunization Administration Document
